@startuml
title Project Aggregate - オブジェクト例（状態バリエーション）

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam objectAttributeIconSize 0

object "プロジェクト: TeamDev 2026 Phase1（進行中）" as project_in_progress <<Project>> {
  id = "55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555"
  title = "TeamDev 2026 Phase1"
  description = "遅延予防アラートMVP"
  dueDate = "2026-04-05"
  status = "in_progress"
  createdAt = "2026-02-01T10:00:00+09:00"
  updatedAt = "2026-03-04T21:00:00+09:00"
}

object "プロジェクト: TeamDev 2025（完了）" as project_completed <<Project>> {
  id = "56666666-6666-6666-6666-666666666666"
  title = "TeamDev 2025"
  dueDate = "2025-12-20"
  status = "completed"
}

object "配属: 開発チームA" as project_team_a <<ProjectTeam>> {
  projectId = "55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555"
  teamId = "33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333"
  assignedAt = "2026-02-02T09:00:00+09:00"
}

object "配属: 開発チームB" as project_team_b <<ProjectTeam>> {
  projectId = "55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555"
  teamId = "34444444-4444-4444-4444-444444444444"
  assignedAt = "2026-02-15T09:00:00+09:00"
}

object "チーム参照A" as team_a <<Team>> {
  id = "33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333"
  name = "開発チームA"
}

object "課題参照" as issue_ref <<Issue>> {
  id = "66666666-6666-6666-6666-666666666666"
  projectId = "55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555"
  status = "in_review"
}

project_in_progress *-- project_team_a
project_in_progress *-- project_team_b
project_team_a -- team_a
project_in_progress -- issue_ref : Issue.projectId

note bottom
Project の in_progress/completed 状態を表現。
ProjectTeam により複数チーム配属を表現。
全日時は Asia/Tokyo（+09:00）。
end note

@enduml